utton\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jxw1665702547126.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jxw1665702547126.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jxw1665702547126.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jxw1665702547126\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Uniface logical that determines the default authentication schema to be used by the web server when processing UHTTP <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SEND</span> requests.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__topic_d137960e1_d137961e1_d137962e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__p_d137963e1_d137964e1_d137965e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">UHTTP_DEF_AUTH</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">B</code> |\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">L</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">N</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__section_hw1_t3f_vvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d397215e74\"> Values </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__ul_ctl_x3f_vvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__li_d48617e1_d48618e1_d48619e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">B</code> for Basic </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__li_d48620e1_d48621e1_d48622e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">L</code> for NTLM </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__li_d48623e1_d48624e1_d48625e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">N</code> for Negotiate, (chooses between NTLM and Kerberos) </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__section_udy_v3f_vvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d397215e101\"> Defaults </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__table_d16394e1_d16395e1_d16396e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Application assignment file </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vcm1665702739978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vcm1665702739978.html\" title=\"Use the [LOGICALS] section of the assignment file to assign values to logicals that can be accessed using the $logical ProcScript function. Each application can have its own set of logicals.\">[LOGICALS]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\"><u class=\"ph u\">B</u></code> if user names are provided in the\n                  UHTTP <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SEND</span> operation  </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__section_f3d_w3f_vvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d397215e167\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__p_d137975e1_d137976e1_d137977e1\">When this logical is set, and the UHTTP\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SEND</span> operation does not specify a user name and password for the web\n        server (URL), the credentials of the current Windows user will be used for authentication.\n        This functionality is not available under Unix.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__p_d137978e1_d137979e1_d137980e1\">If this logical is omitted, and the\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SEND</span> operation specifies a user name but no authentication scheme,\n        Basic authentication is used.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxw1665702547126__p_d137981e1_d137982e1_d137983e1\">The default authentication scheme can be overridden by\n        specifying a scheme in the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Username</var> parameter of the UHTTP\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SEND</span> operation.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/unt1665702546031.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>SEND</a><p>Send an HTTP request.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/luk1665703181080.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Authentication with UHTTP</a><p>The UHTTP component is used to send requests to a web server, often via a proxy server. One or both servers may require user credentials to authenticate the request.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529098\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529098\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UHTTP_DEF_AUTH Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface logical that determines the default authentication schema to be used by the web server when processing UHTTP SEND requests. UHTTP_DEF_AUTH { = } B | L | N Values B for Basic L for NTLM N for Negotiate, (chooses between NTLM and Kerberos) Defaults Assignment file: Application assignment file Section: [LOGICALS] Default value: B if user names are provided in the UHTTP SEND operation Description When this logical is set, and the UHTTP SEND operation does not specify a user name and password for the web server (URL), the credentials of the current Windows user will be used for authentication. This functionality is not available under Unix. If this logical is omitted, and the SEND operation specifies a user name but no authentication scheme, Basic authentication is used. The default authentication scheme can be overridden by specifying a scheme in the Username parameter of the UHTTP SEND operation. Related Links SEND Send an HTTP request. Authentication with UHTTP The UHTTP component is used to send requests to a web server, often via a proxy server. One or both servers may require user credentials to authenticate the request. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}